CFS Memory Dwell Commands

The Memory Dwell Application has the following commands:

Global MD_NOOP_CC
Memory Dwell No-Op Command

Global MD_RESET_CNTRS_CC
Memory Dwell Reset Counters Command

Global MD_START_DWELL_CC
Memory Dwell Start Dwell Command

Global MD_STOP_DWELL_CC
Memory Dwell Stop Dwell Command

Global MD_JAM_DWELL_CC
Jam Dwell
